item.title: CVE-2021-24511|2024-08-03T19:35:20.158Z -- unknown -- product%20feed%20on%20woocommerce%20for%20google%2C%20awin%2C%20shareasale%2C%20bing%2C%20and%20more
item.description: The fetch_product_ajax functionality in the Product Feed on WooCommerce WordPress plugin before 3.3.1.0 uses a `product_id` POST parameter which is not properly sanitised, escaped or validated before inserting to a SQL statement, leading to SQL injection.
